{"tid":2158334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Connect】誠懇呼籲唔好再舉呢兩支旗","createTime":"2020-08-15T15:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T21:48:34.000Z","uid":154486,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"38cf507dfa2a3eed4f7fa8471bef662680e210ca","tid":2158334,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T15:57:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">白羅斯</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wL2TP9v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwL2TP9v.jpg&h=9ce7ebe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsource國際文宣組tg<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LDZKWQY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLDZKWQY.png&h=69f62d08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1991年白羅斯自蘇聯獨立後，<strong>曾於1992年立法恢復使用1918年至1920年白羅斯人民共和國時的白紅白雙色三條式國旗。<br />\n</strong><br />\n直到1995年因為<strong>白羅斯強人總統<ins>盧卡申科</ins>的親俄背景，改採白俄羅斯蘇維埃社會主義共和國國旗</strong>，將該旗稍做修改（取消蘇聯時期的金色鐮刀錘子及金邊紅色五角星圖案）後即成為現在的樣式。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nPoPoxr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnPoPoxr.jpg&h=bce8df80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%99%BD%E4%BF%84%E7%BD%97%E6%96%AF%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2599%25BD%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BD%2597%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%259B%25BD%25E6%2597%2597&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9ELzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=545caf4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%99%BD%E4%BF%84%E7%BD%97%E6%96%AF%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%97</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"green\">伊朗</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPdWNZ9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPdWNZ9.jpg&h=cabac68b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yvRtD7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyvRtD7d.png&h=611012f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xk1ELNx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxk1ELNx.png&h=dddf0e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三色起於卡扎爾王朝，但中間的圖案為獅子與太陽，沿用至伊朗伊斯蘭革命為止。這面旗也為反對伊斯蘭共和國的人士所用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%259B%25BD%25E6%2597%2597&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9ELzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=af8201da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%97</a><br />\n<br />\n二十世紀時，部分政治家和學者建議將諸如卡維之旗等其他物品設為國家象徵，替代獅日。但是該標誌卻一直擔任伊朗國家象徵，直到1979年革命時獅子與太陽才被從公共場合和政府組織標識中抹去，代之以現在的伊朗國徽。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%8B%AE%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%8E%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%258B%25AE%25E5%25AD%2590%25E4%25B8%258E%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E9%2598%25B3&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9ELzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=c80e492b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%8B%AE%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%8E%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">呢兩幅旗都係外國勢力反白亂伊既旗<br />\n大家千祈唔好因為手痕以為人地唔識就Print出黎周圍貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"3193ceb62daf11c1d84ae074d52d1345289aa157","tid":2158334,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T15:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7196919709792bfb691b57888fd5ef1c0416fbf","tid":2158334,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T15:59:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj